
### Config file for generic radiative equilibrium test
#
REQUIRES Driver
REQUIRES physics/Hydro/HydroMain/unsplit/Hydro_Unsplit
REQUIRES Grid/GridMain/paramesh/paramesh4/Paramesh4dev

### Importing the Monte Carlo RHD module
REQUIRES physics/MonteCarloRHD/MonteCarloRHDMain/NonIonizingRad




### Simulation specific runtime parameters
D sim_pAmbient       Initial ambient pressure
PARAMETER sim_pAmbient     REAL    1.E-13

D sim_rhoAmbient     Initial ambient density
PARAMETER sim_rhoAmbient   REAL    7.78e-10

D sim_tempAmbient    Intial ambient temperature
PARAMETER sim_tempAmbient  REAL    10.0

D sim_bulkvelaxis    Direction for the bulk velocity
PARAMETER sim_bulkvelaxis  INTEGER 1

D sim_bulkvelval     Value of the bulk velocity
PARAMETER sim_bulkvelval  REAL  1.0e6

